elements.name: I want to verify that I can receive and play audio files 0

steps.name: There is a team owner "user1Name" with team "Audio"
User user1Name adds users user2Name to team "Audio" with role Member
User user1Name adds a new device Device1 with label Device1
User user2Name is me
User user1Name has group conversation SendYourAudioHere with user2Name in team "Audio"
I see Welcome Page
I open staging backend deep link
I tap proceed button on custom backend alert
I tap login button on Welcome Page
I sign in using my email
I tap login button on email Login Page
I wait until I am fully logged in
I decline share data alert
I see conversation "SendYourAudioHere" in conversation list
I tap on conversation name "SendYourAudioHere" in conversation list
User user1Name sends local audio file named "test.m4a" via device Device1 to group conversation "SendYourAudioHere"
I see an audio file in the conversation view
I see the time played in the audio file is 00:00
I tap play button on the audio file
I wait for 10 seconds
I tap pause button on the audio file
I see the time played in the audio file is not 00:00
